sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Shop as Shop Frontend
    participant Manager as Widget Manager

    User->>Shop: 1. Enters Product Page
    Shop->>Manager: Instantiate TecsafeWidgetManager
    Shop->>Manager: .createProductDetailWidget()
    Note over Manager: Widget is active and displayed

    User->>Shop: 2. Navigates to another Product Page
    Shop->>Manager: .destroy() on old widget <br> or <br> .destroyAll() on manager <br> depending on implementation
    Shop->>Manager: .createProductDetailWidget()
    Note over Manager: New widget replaces the old one

    User->>Shop: 3. Clicks Login
    Shop->>Shop: Shows modal and completes async login
    Shop->>Manager: .refreshToken()
    Note over Manager: Updates configuration session in background

    User->>Shop: 4. Clicks Logout
    Shop->>Shop: Completes async logout
    Shop->>Manager: .refreshToken()
    Note over Manager: Downgrades back to a guest session

    User->>Shop: 5. Leaves Shop (e.g. goes to Checkout)
    Shop->>Manager: .destroyAll()
    Note over Manager: Cleans up all timeouts and memory
